ActRoyal Canadian Mounted Police Act
SubjectAgreement Respecting Biology Casework Analysis -All other provinces
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness to enter into the AGREEMENT RESPECTING BIOLOGY CASEWORK ANALYSIS with the governments of the provinces of British Columbia, Alberta, Saskatchewan, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Nova Scotia, Prince Edward Island and Newfoundland and Labrador, and the governments of Yukon, the Northwest Territories, and Nunavut, which provides funding for biology casework analysis, effective April 1, 2010 to March 31, 2012, with the possibility of three additional one-year renewal periods for fiscal years 2012/13, 2013/14, and 2014/15.
